The error shows that you have the slf4j interface library added but the slf4j implementation is missing. So you have to add either `slf4j-log4j12` or `slf4j-simple`.

```xml
&lt;dependency&gt;
  &lt;groupId&gt;org.slf4j&lt;/groupId&gt;
  &lt;artifactId&gt;slf4j-api&lt;/artifactId&gt;
  &lt;version&gt;${slf4j.version}&lt;/version&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;
&lt;dependency&gt;
  &lt;groupId&gt;org.slf4j&lt;/groupId&gt;
  &lt;artifactId&gt;slf4j-log4j12&lt;/artifactId&gt;
  &lt;version&gt;${slf4j.version}&lt;/version&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;
```
OR
```xml
&lt;dependency&gt;
  &lt;groupId&gt;org.slf4j&lt;/groupId&gt;
  &lt;artifactId&gt;slf4j-api&lt;/artifactId&gt;
  &lt;version&gt;${slf4j.version}&lt;/version&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;
&lt;dependency&gt;
  &lt;groupId&gt;org.slf4j&lt;/groupId&gt;
  &lt;artifactId&gt;slf4j-simple&lt;/artifactId&gt;
  &lt;version&gt;${slf4j.version}&lt;/version&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;
```

Where `${slf4j.version}` is the version of your slf4j library.

